data.text: @brooklynnn_ all my cousins who have had it just said to keep up with ibuprofen and they felt fine!! just more severe aches than the first round👍🏼
@brooklynnn_ I was sick for 24 hours....fever, chills, body aches. After sleeping it off, I felt 💯 fine!!!
@brooklynnn_ My boyfriend & mom are both fully vaccinated! Mom was totally fine after the second shot, my boyfriend had a headache and a slight fever the next day but it only lasted 24 hours
@brooklynnn_ I have heard good stuff from people that didn't have Covid previously. Now the folks that had covid have said it's like getting the flu but for like 24 hrs
@brooklynnn_ My mom is a nurse so she has a pretty good immune system and rarely gets sick but I’d just prepare for anything just in case! I’ve seen a lot on tik tok too
